"          ◦ Mountains of Haag\n"
"          ◦ Green Forest\n"
"          ◦ Silent Forest\n"
"          ◦ Forest of Thelien\n"
"          ◦ River Oumph\n"
"          ◦ River Bork\n"
"          ◦ Wild Steppe"
